for programmers to test out their commmodities.

@item Update
The list will be updated.

@item Print
This function allows you to send the list to
printer or a selected file.

@item Priority
This function allows you to change the priority of a commodity.

@item Remove
Removes the selected commodity from the system. Please try a frienly
remove before, using @samp{Kill}. Maybe the commodity removes itself
voluntarily. =;^)

@item More
Opens a window with further information.

@item Exit
Closes the window.
@end table
