@samp{OpenC} is zero.

@item Remove
The selected library will be removed with this function provided that
no program uses this library anymore and the @samp{OpenC} is zero.

Some libraries can't be removed from system without a reset.  So you
shouldn't wonder about it, if this happens.

@item Functions
All library function offsets and addresses are shown up in a subwindow.
If an appropriate @file{.fd} file exists and an @file{FD:} assign points
to its directory, then you will also see the function names.

@item Update
The list of libraries will be updated.

@item Print
This function allows you to send the list of @samp{Libraries} to
printer or a selected file.
@item More
